Lynne Roberts https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynne_Roberts 0 Lynne Roberts, also credited as Mary Hart, was born Theda May Roberts (November 22, 1922 – April 1, 1978). She was an American film actress during the Golden Age of Hollywood who appeared exclusively in what were referred to as B-movies.
